TITLE: Uniqueness Modifier for Pizza NFT in Solidity
DESCRIPTION: A modifier to ensure a Pizza NFT is unique before creation. Checks existing pizzas and compares their names and DNA against the proposed new values. Uses keccak256 hash for string comparison.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
modifier isUnique(string memory _name, uint256 _dna) {
    bool result = true;
    for (uint256 i = 0; i < pizzas.length; i++) {
        if (
            keccak256(abi.encodePacked(pizzas[i].name)) ==
            keccak256(abi.encodePacked(_name)) &&
            pizzas[i].dna == _dna
        ) {
            result = false;
        }
    }
    require(result, "Pizza with such name already exists.");
    _;
}
```

