16   | AND            | a, b         | a && b                           | bitwise AND
17   | OR             | a, b         | a || b                           | bitwise OR
18   | XOR            | a, b         | a ^ b                            | bitwise XOR
19   | NOT            | a            | ~a                               | bitwise NOT
1A   | BYTE           | i, x         | (x >> (248 - i * 8)) && 0xFF     | ith byte of (u)int256 x, from the left
