TITLE: Calculating Average Daily Block Production on Ethereum
DESCRIPTION: This SQL query calculates the average number of blocks produced per day on Ethereum. It uses a Common Table Expression (CTE) to first count blocks by day, then calculates the average of those daily counts.

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
WITH temp_table AS (
SELECT
    DATE_TRUNC('day', time) AS dt,
    COUNT(*) AS block_count
FROM ethereum."blocks"
GROUP BY dt
OFFSET 1
)
SELECT
    AVG(block_count) AS avg_block_count
FROM temp_table
```

