TITLE: Retrieving Average Daily Gas Limit in Ethereum Blocks
DESCRIPTION: SQL query that retrieves the average gas limit per day for Ethereum blocks. This query helps visualize the supply side of Ethereum's block space, showing how the maximum capacity of blocks has changed over time.

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT
    DATE_TRUNC('day', time) AS dt,
    AVG(gas_limit) AS avg_block_gas_limit
FROM ethereum."blocks"
GROUP BY dt
OFFSET 1
```

