TITLE: Testing Cache Deduplication in Solidity
DESCRIPTION: Test function that verifies the cache doesn't duplicate values by writing the same value multiple times and ensuring that the key remains the same.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
    // Cache the same value multiple times, ensure that the key stays
    // the same
    function testRepeatCaching() public {
        for(uint i=1; i<100; i++) {
            uint _key1 = cache.cacheWrite(i);
            uint _key2 = cache.cacheWrite(i);
            assertEq(_key1, _key2);
        }
        for(uint i=1; i<100; i+=3) {
            uint _key = cache.cacheWrite(i);
            assertEq(_key, i);
        }
    }    // testRepeatCaching
```

