TITLE: Incrementor Contract with Assertion for Testing
DESCRIPTION: The Incrementor contract modified to include an assert statement to verify that the value of tmp is always less than or equal to counter after incrementing.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
contract Incrementor {
  uint private counter = 2**200;

  function inc(uint val) public returns (uint){
    uint tmp = counter;
    counter += val;
    assert (tmp <= counter);
    return (counter - tmp);
  }
}
```

