TITLE: Defining ERC-20 Events in Interface
DESCRIPTION: Declares the Transfer and Approval events that ERC-20 tokens must emit when state changes occur. These events allow external applications to track token movements and allowance changes on the blockchain.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
    /**
     * @dev Emitted when `value` tokens are moved from one account (`from`) to
     * another (`to`).
     *
     * Note that `value` may be zero.
     */
