TITLE: Implementing Emergency Stop Pattern in Solidity Smart Contracts
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates a pattern for implementing an emergency stop mechanism in Ethereum smart contracts. It includes Boolean flags to control contract state, function modifiers to restrict access during emergencies, and functions to stop and resume contract operations.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
