TITLE: Ensuring Pizza Token Uniqueness in Solidity
DESCRIPTION: Modifier that ensures a Pizza token is unique by checking if a token with the same name and DNA already exists. It iterates through all existing tokens and compares their name hashes and DNA values.

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
modifier isUnique(string memory _name, uint256 _dna) {
        bool result = true;
        for (uint256 i = 0; i < pizzas.length; i++) {
            if (
                keccak256(abi.encodePacked(pizzas[i].name)) ==
                keccak256(abi.encodePacked(_name)) &&
                pizzas[i].dna == _dna
            ) {
                result = false;
            }
        }
        require(result, "Pizza with such name already exists.");
        _;
    }
```

