TITLE: Querying Gas Prices Paid to Ethereum Foundation
DESCRIPTION: This SQL query examines transactions sent to the Ethereum Foundation's address, showing the gas prices paid and ETH sent over time. It converts gas prices to Gwei and ETH values to their standard units.

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT
    block_time,
    gas_price / 1e9 AS gas_price_gwei,
    value / 1e18 AS eth_sent
FROM ethereum."transactions"
WHERE "to" = '\xde0B295669a9FD93d5F28D9Ec85E40f4cb697BAe'
ORDER BY block_time DESC
```

