TITLE: Calculating Daily Ethereum Blocks (Math in Markdown)
DESCRIPTION: Formula for calculating the number of Ethereum blocks produced in a day based on a 12-second block time. This calculation shows how 7,200 blocks are produced daily.

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
- `(1 bloco/12 segundos) * (60 segundos/minuto) = 5 blocos/minuto`
- `(5 blocos/minuto) * (60 minutos/hora) = 300 blocos/hora`
